%% MCL Visual Decision Support — Mermaid fallback source
%% v1.5.4 — MHA-MCL-2026-v1.5.4-DRAFT
%% Independent educational synthesis. Not externally endorsed.
%% Three diagrams below: first-line algorithm, pathway-at-a-glance, access status.

%% ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% A. First-Line Treatment Algorithm
%% ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
flowchart TD
    A["1. NEW MCL DIAGNOSIS"]:::start
    B["2. Confirm minimum dataset<br/>• Tissue diagnosis<br/>• Morphology<br/>• Ki-67 (percentage)<br/>• TP53 — IHC AND NGS<br/>• MIPI / MIPI-c"]:::box
    C{"Indolent / non-nodal<br/>AND asymptomatic?"}:::diamond
    OBS["Observe<br/>Watch & wait"]:::green
    D{"Fit for intensive /<br/>cytarabine-based induction?"}:::diamond
    F1["A. Current UK standard<br/>R-CHOP / R-DHAP cytarabine<br/>± ASCT consolidation<br/>+ rituximab maintenance"]:::green
    F2["B. Evolving / access-dependent<br/>TRIANGLE ibrutinib-integrated<br/>induction + 2-yr maintenance<br/>Where legitimate access exists"]:::amber
    O1["A. Current UK standard<br/>Bendamustine-rituximab (BR)<br/>± rituximab maintenance<br/>R-CHOP if BR contraindicated"]:::green
    O2["B. Evolving / access-dependent<br/>Acalabrutinib + BR (ECHO)<br/>NICE GID-TA11091 in dev<br/>Not routine until final guidance"]:::amber
    HR["High-Risk Biology Overlay<br/>TP53 / blastoid / pleomorphic /<br/>high Ki-67 / high MIPI-c /<br/>complex karyotype<br/>→ Trial discussion<br/>→ BTKi access route<br/>→ Early CAR-T pathway mapping"]:::red
    DOC["5. Document at MDT<br/>• Evidence basis<br/>• Access / funding route<br/>• Alternatives and toxicity<br/>• Patient preference and consent"]:::start

    A --> B
    B --> C
    C -->|YES| OBS
    C -->|NO| D
    D -->|FIT| F1
    F1 --> F2
    D -->|OLDER / LESS FIT| O1
    O1 --> O2
    F2 -.->|overlay| HR
    O2 -.->|overlay| HR
    HR --> DOC

    classDef start fill:#7a1f2b,stroke:#7a1f2b,color:#fff,font-weight:700;
    classDef box fill:#ffffff,stroke:#7a1f2b,color:#1a1a1a;
    classDef diamond fill:#fff5f6,stroke:#7a1f2b,color:#1a1a1a;
    classDef green fill:#e8f4ec,stroke:#2e6b3e,color:#1a1a1a;
    classDef amber fill:#fdf5e3,stroke:#b08538,color:#1a1a1a;
    classDef red fill:#fdecec,stroke:#8b2e2e,color:#1a1a1a;


